data.description: Just reduced $10,000!! Make an offer today! This rarely available Oxon Run Hills semi-detached all brick home is ready for a new tenant! You are greeted by beautiful hardwood floors on the main level when entering into the sun-filled living room. Hardwoods flow through the dining room which is adjacent to the galley kitchen which features granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and access to the huge backyard. Stairs to the basement level split with a half bath at the landing.   The wide-open lower level is perfect for relaxing, game room, or theater room. Utilities, laundry, and storage space area are also found on this level. Upper-level features 3 bright bedrooms with hardwood floors and a full bath. Driveway for 2 cars plus ample street parking. Conveniently located close to shopping and major commuter routes - Routes 5, Capital Beltway, and Suitland Parkway. Write an offer today while rates are still relatively low and settle into your new home for the holidays.
